tweight and&nbsp;<div>portable with no cords or&nbsp;<div>complicated sensor pads.</div></div></H4>\n                </div>\n            \n                <div class=\"large-3 small-12 text-center\">\n                    <div class=\"home-icon\" \n                     style=\"background-image:url('https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/unique_selling_point/img/749835fc88.png')\">\n                    </div>\n                    <H4>Monitors your&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: initial;\">little&nbsp;</span><div><span style=\"background-color: initial;\">one’s movements</span></div></H4>\n                </div>\n            \n                <div class=\"large-3 small-12 text-center\">\n                    <div class=\"home-icon\" \n                     style=\"background-image:url('https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/unique_selling_point/img/414d1a8f76.png')\">\n                    </div>\n                    <H4>Easy to use and simply&nbsp;<div>clips onto diaper/nappy</div></H4>\n                </div>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n        \n    </section>\n\n    <section  id=\"home_blocks\">\n        \n        \n<div class=\"home-blocks\">\n    <div class=\"grid-container\">\n        \n            \n                <div class=\"grid-x\">\n                    <div class=\"small-12 text-center show-for-small-only\">\n                        <img src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/block/img/98983e5e44.png'/>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 text-small-center text-medium-center text-large-center text-center text-left small-text-center\">\n                        <br class=\"hide-for-small-only\"><br class=\"hide-for-small-only\">\n                        \n                            <h2>SNUZA PICO 2</h2>\n                        \n                        \n                            <h1>MONITOR YOUR&nbsp;<div>CHILD USING SMART TECHNOLOGY</div></h1>\n                        \n                        \n                            <p>With Pico 2, you can monitor your child's movements, sleep patterns, skin temperature, body position and more.</p>\n                        \n                        \n                            <a class=\"button upper\" href=\"/product/pico2/\">Learn More</a>\n                        \n                        \n                    </div>\n                    \n                        <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 text-small-center text-medium-center text-large-center text-center text-center hide-for-small-only\">\n                            <img style=\"position: relative; top: 50px;\" src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/block/img/98983e5e44.png'/>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n                <div class=\"grid-x\"><hr class=\"small-12 large-12 medium-12\"/></div>\n            \n        \n            \n                <div class=\"grid-x\">\n                    <div class=\"small-12 text-center show-for-small-only\">\n                        <img src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/block/img/902a1515ce.png'/>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                        <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 text-small-center text-medium-center text-large-center text-center text-center hide-for-small-only\">\n                            <img src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/block/img/902a1515ce.png'/>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 text-small-center text-medium-center text-large-center text-center text-left small-text-center\">\n                        <br class=\"hide-for-small-only\"><br class=\"hide-for-small-only\">\n                        \n                            <h2>Snuza HERO<sup><sup class=\"text-ss\">MD</sup></sup></h2>\n                        \n                        \n                            <h1>KNOW IF YOUR BABY STOPS BREATHING</h1>\n                        \n                        \n                            <p>Snuza Hero<sup><sup class=\"text-ss\">MD</sup></sup> is the first portably, Medically Certified baby breathing monitor in Europe and has been clinically proven to detect cessation of breathing in infants.</p>\n                        \n                        \n                            <a class=\"button upper\" href=\"/product/hero-md/\">Learn More</a>\n                        \n                        \n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n                <div class=\"grid-x\"><hr class=\"small-12 large-12 medium-12\"/></div>\n            \n        \n            \n                <div class=\"grid-x\">\n                    <div class=\"small-12 text-center show-for-small-only\">\n                        <img src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/block/img/ba065b26d8.png'/>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 text-small-center text-medium-center text-large-center text-center text-left small-text-center\">\n                        <br class=\"hide-for-small-only\"><br class=\"hide-for-small-only\">\n                        \n                            <h2>Snuza HERO<sup><sup class=\"text-ss\">SE</sup></sup></h2>\n                        \n                        \n                            <h1>HIGHLY RATED BABY MONITOR ON AMAZON</h1>\n                        \n                        \n                            <p>Snuza Hero<sup class=\"text-ss\">SE</sup> will monitor your baby's movements while your baby sleeps and alarm if no movement is detected. It's lightweight, portable and fits in the palm of your hand.</p>\n                        \n                        \n                            <a class=\"button upper\" href=\"/product/hero-se/\">Learn More</a>\n                        \n                        \n                    </div>\n                    \n                        <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 text-small-center text-medium-center text-large-center text-center text-center hide-for-small-only\">\n                            <img style=\"position: relative; top: 50px;\" src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/block/img/ba065b26d8.png'/>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n                <div class=\"grid-x\"><hr class=\"small-12 large-12 medium-12\"/></div>\n            \n        \n            \n                <div class=\"grid-x\">\n                    <div class=\"small-12 text-center show-for-small-only\">\n                        <img src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/block/img/7ece95e93c.png'/>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                        <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 text-small-center text-medium-center text-large-center text-center text-center hide-for-small-only\">\n                            <img src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/webserver.snuza.com/block/img/7ece95e93c.png'/>\n                        </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 text-small-center text-medium-center text-large-center text-center text-left small-text-center\">\n                        <br class=\"hide-for-small-only\"><br class=\"hide-for-small-only\">\n                        \n                            <h2>SNUZA GO!<sup><sup class=\"text-ss\">SE</sup></sup></h2>\n                        \n                        \n                            <h1>GET PEACE OF MIND WITH SNUZA GO!<sup><sup class=\"text-ss\">SE</sup></sup></h1>\n                        \n                        \n                            <p>Snuza Go!<span class=\"text-ss\" style=\"font-size: 13.2px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -8.36px;\"><sup class=\"text-ss\">SE</sup></span>&nbsp;will alarm if your baby breathing motion stops. Adjustable alarm settings.</p>\n                        \n                        \n                            <a class=\"button upper\" href=\"/product/go/\">Learn More</a>\n                        \n                        \n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n                <div class=\"grid-x\"><hr class=\"small-12 large-12 medium-12\"/></div>\n            \n        \n    </div>\n</div>\n        \n    </section>\n\n    <section  id=\"home_reviews\">\n        \n        \n    <div class=\"grid-container\">\n        <div class=\"large-12 small-12 text-center\">\n            <h1 class=\"text-center\">Top Reviews</h1>\n            \n                <div class=\"quote\">\n                    \n                        <h4>J WRIGHT</h4>\n                        <p>I've never yet written an Amazon review for a product, but after 3 months of faultless nightly use of this tiny device, I felt I had to share. Like many parents, I found myself worrying about SIDS, and waking in a panic multiple times a night to check my newborn was still breathing. I cannot express the reassurance this little device has offered me - now if I wake at night, I can simply listen to the quiet \"tick-tick\" (or silent flashing light, if you prefer) and know that all is well.</p>\n                    \n                </div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"grid-x text-center\">\n                        <hr class=\"large-6 small-12 medium-8\"/>\n                    </div>\n                \n            \n                <div class=\"quote\">\n                    \n                        <h4>LAURA GREGORY</h4>\n                        <p>I am a Paramedic and was worried about SIDS and I found it really hard to relax and sleep properly when my baby was asleep. The device slides onto a nappy, and gives off a light each time the baby breaths. This light can normally been seen through clothes, so you can see it easily in the dark. The sensitivity is good and the alarm is loud so you can hear it if you're sleeping next to the baby. I sleep when my baby sleeps now.</p>\n                    \n                </div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"grid-x text-center\">\n                        <hr class=\"large-6 small-12 medium-8\"/>\n                    </div>\n                \n            \n                <div class=\"quote\">\n                    \n                        <h4>KC</h4>\n                        <p>We originally tried the much more expensive sock-based competitor, which was absolutely terrible; ridden w/ false alarms and much too complicated for our preference. That got returned, and we tried this instead. The Snuza Hero<span class=\"text-ss\" style=\"font-size: 10.8px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -6.84px;\"><sup class=\"text-ss\">SE</sup></span>&nbsp;works wonderfully, and is extremely simple. No apps, no connection issues, no repeated false alarms... just pure functionality. I'd recommend this to any parent.</p>\n                    \n                </div>\n                \n            \n        </div>\n        <div class=\"large-12 small-12 text-center\">\n            <a href=\"/reviews-testimonials/\" class=\"button upper\">See what our parents say</a>\n            <hr class=\"hide-for-small-only\">\n        </div>\n    </div>\n        \n    </section>\n\n    <section  id=\"home_blogs\">\n        \n        \n\n<div class=\"home-blogs\">\n    <div class=\"grid-container\">\n        <div class=\"grid-x\">\n            <div class=\"small-12 cell\">\n                <h2 class=\"text-center\">Our Parenting Blog</h2>\n                <h3 class=\"text-center\">Written for Parents By Parents</h3>\n                <div class=\"hide-for-small-only\">\n                    <br>&nbsp;\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid